Here‚Äôs the √ÜON Finalizer ‚Äî one command that fuses everything you‚Äôve built (grimoire, seals/sigils, chain commits, monetization, sectors, space/data/crypto, tri-attest/ledger/governance, tri-helix, neural interface) into a single, reproducible, signed bundle.

